e (Ypres)|Gravenstafel Ridge]] near [[Saint-Julien, Langemark|Saint-Julian]], [[Western Front (World War I)|Belgium]] on 23 April 1915 on the second day of the [[Second Battle of Ypres]]. <ref name=\"SSH\" /> He is commemorated on the [[Menin Gate]] and the [[Saint Julien Memorial|Saint-Julian Memorial]].<ref name=\"SSH\" /><ref name=\"CWGC\">{{CWGC|id=1591941|accessdate=30 July 2016}}</ref>\n\n== Honours ==\n'''Dunblane'''\n* Perthshire Cup: 1905\u201306<ref name=\"SSH\" />\n\n== Career statistics ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\n! rowspan=\"2\" |Club\n! rowspan=\"2\" |Season\n! colspan=\"3\" |League\n! colspan=\"2\" |Scottish Cup\n! colspan=\"2\" |Total\n|-\n!Division\n!Apps\n!Goals\n!Apps\n!Goals\n!Apps\n!Goals\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" |[[Queen's Park F.C.|Queen's Park]]\n|[[1902\u201303 Scottish Division One|1902\u201303]]<ref name=\"QPFC\">{{Cite web |url=http://www.qpfc.com/appearances/e/eadieaw.htm |title=QPFC.com \u2013 A Historical Queen's Park FC Website |website=www.qpfc.com |accessdate=4 June 2017}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"3\" |[[Scottish Football League First Division|Scottish First Division]]\n|2\n|0\n|0\n|0\n|2\n|0\n|-\n|[[1904\u201305 Scottish Division One|1904\u201305]]<ref name=\"QPFC\" />\n|8\n|0\n|1\n|0\n|9\n|0\n|-\n|[[1905\u201306 Scottish Division One|1905\u201306]]<ref name=\"QPFC\" />\n|2\n|0\n|0\n|0\n|2\n|0\n|-\n! colspan=\"2\" |Total\n!12\n!0\n!1\n!0\n!13\n!0\n|-\n|[[St Mirren F.C.|St Mirren]]\n|[[1906\u201307 Scottish Division One|1906\u201307]]<ref name=\"Litster\">{{Cite book |title=Record of Pre-War Scottish League Players |last=Litster |first=John |publisher=PM Publications |location=Norwich}}</ref>\n|Scottish First Division\n|1\n|0\n|0\n|0\n|1\n|0\n|-\n|[[Partick Thistle F.C.|Partick Thistle]]\n|[[1908\u201309 Scottish Division One|1908\u201309]]<ref name=\"Litster\" />\n|Scottish First Division\n|5\n|0\n|0\n|0\n|5\n|0\n|-\n! colspan=\"3\" |Career total\n!18\n!0\n!1\n!0\n!19\n!0\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{